üìå AGENT-SPECIFIC INSTRUCTIONS
For AI Code Editors/Agents:
On Task Start:
Acknowledge receipt of these rules
Confirm understanding of the 21-step framework
Ask clarifying questions for ambiguous requirements
Estimate time for task completion
Identify dependencies and potential blockers
Update risk register with new risks
During Task:
Follow all 21 steps in sequence
Document decisions and reasoning
Update progress tracker in real-time
Flag issues immediately (don't wait until end)
Request code review before step 21
Run all automated checks
On Task Completion:
Complete entire code review checklist
Verify all benchmarks met
Update documentation
Create detailed commit message
Mark status as ‚úì only after step 21
Report completion with metrics summary
Red Flags to Report:
Any step taking 3x longer than estimated
Blockers that prevent progress
Security vulnerabilities discovered
Performance targets cannot be met
Test coverage below 80%
Accessibility issues found

