üìñ GLOSSARY
Term
Definition
FCP
First Contentful Paint - time to first content render
LCP
Largest Contentful Paint - time to main content render
TTI
Time to Interactive - when page becomes fully interactive
CLS
Cumulative Layout Shift - visual stability metric
FID
First Input Delay - interactivity metric
WCAG
Web Content Accessibility Guidelines
OWASP
Open Web Application Security Project
DRY
Don't Repeat Yourself principle
SRP
Single Responsibility Principle
CI/CD
Continuous Integration/Continuous Deployment
APM
Application Performance Monitoring


